;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;movement&nbsp;=&nbsp;Vector3.ClampMagnitude(movement,&nbsp;speed);&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 130, 0); background-color: inherit;\">//将对角移动的速度限制为和沿着轴移动的速度一样</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;movement.y&nbsp;=&nbsp;gravity;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;movement&nbsp;*=&nbsp;Time.deltaTime;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;movement&nbsp;=&nbsp;transform.TransformDirection(movement);&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 130, 0); background-color: inherit;\">//把movement向量从本地变换为全局坐标</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;_charController.Move(movement);&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"comment\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 130, 0); background-color: inherit;\">//告知CharacterController通过movement向量移动</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: inherit;\">}&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></li></ol><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '游戏 game unity3d', '5');
INSERT INTO `t_blog` VALUES ('54', '程序员上下班途中都在想什么', '程序员工作的城市一般都是在北京、上海、广州、深圳、杭州等大城市，上班路途都得一个小时左右，那程序员坐车都在想什么呢？1.看马路汽车一般上班高峰时间都是有很多车的，如果每天都能记住每天大部分的车辆信息你就会发现同一时间、地点会发现同一辆车，这些车一般都是老司机开的班车，他们的职责就是按时把员工送到公司，所以每天', '2018-03-07 11:37:00', '0', '0', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://ss.csdn.net/p?http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/foPACGrddJ1iaCkSbQbyY8y5JpfPM7Vm5OH947lOFkGoluvJJ3Ag4rN4THnDQUqlJbHgyicY2YaAOpyGxGKNW8nw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">程序员工作的城市一般都是在北京、上海、广州、深圳、杭州等大城市，上班路途都得一个小时左右，那程序员坐车都在想什么呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;\">1.看马路汽车</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">一般上班高峰时间都是有很多车的，如果每天都能记住每天大部分的车辆信息你就会发现同一时间、地点会发现同一辆车，这些车一般都是老司机开的班车，他们的职责就是按时把员工送到公司，所以每天同一时间、地点看到同一辆车也不足为奇。每天在同一路段看到同一辆车心中会欣喜一下自己的判断“这车果然在这相遇”，如果那一天在同一路段如果没看到那辆车心中会想出一堆可能，改时间了、堵车了等等，也会继续在路上继续搜寻那辆没有的车，心中还有一点小失落。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;\">2.看车上乘客</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">早上公交车一般还算准点，所以一些人早上都会赶固定的一趟公交或者地铁，这样就很容易发现熟悉的面孔，每个人上车站牌、下车站牌、喜欢站的位置基本都是固定的，因为习惯了就不自觉的做出同样的行为。经常看一个人就会根据这个人上车的站台猜住在哪个小区、下车的站台猜去哪上班、穿衣风格猜是什么职业、每天手里多一样东西都会不自觉的看上一眼，打电话说话也会注意一点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;\">3.看电视剧</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">公交车看电视剧一般都是女生喜欢做的事情，每天晚上下载好要追得电视剧，第二天坐车无聊时看一看。看电视剧旁边的乘客一般也会看上几眼是什么电视剧，女生一般习惯了也不会在意。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">4.玩游戏</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">公交车一起玩游戏那可是相当开心的事情了，几个人坐在车上一起玩游戏一会时间就过去了，即使站着一天的疲倦也都没了，下车还得惋惜一下没玩够啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">5.睡觉</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">公交车睡觉可是一个技术活啊，在那么嘈杂的环境还能睡着实属不易啊，而且睡觉时间还要掌握好，到站之前准定醒，半睡半醒之间度过下班拥堵的交通时间还是很享受的啊。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);\">6.沉思</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">公交车沉思的也是占一部分，看着窗外的景象，想想自己的未来，想想假期怎么度过、想想回到家的幸福时刻，估计都会想着想着不自觉的笑出来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img class=\"img_loading\" src=\"http://ss.csdn.net/p?http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/foPACGrddJ1iaCkSbQbyY8y5JpfPM7Vm5uP4QgIYLsSejsvFUkWa9c00tYzoZhFAP5icL82oFsApYwPmF6mjzYEQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" alt=\"640?wx_fmt=jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">两点一线的生活还是很规律的，每天上下班坐车的时间估计是想的最少的了，没有了工作的压力、家庭的烦恼，想的就是这一路的事情，可以尽情放空自己，给自己一个休息的时间，上班路途虽然遥远，但路还是有终点的，前方虽然不都是光明但也有足够的理由让我们去追求。所以在大城市上班的程序员路上的时间还是可以好好利用的，虽然没有小县城那样开车悠闲的十多分钟到家，但大城市能教会我们的还是有很多的，虽然苦点但人生是有意义的。时间就像海绵里的水，只要愿意挤，总还是有的。所以在大城市的小伙伴们加油！</span></p><p><br/></p>', '工作 休息', '2');

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for t_blogger
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `t_blogger`;
CREATE TABLE `t_blogger` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '博主id',
  `username` varchar(50) NOT NULL COMMENT '博主姓名',
  `password` varchar(100) NOT NULL COMMENT '博主密码',
  `profile` text COMMENT '博主信息',
  `nickname` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '博主昵称',
  `sign` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '博主签名',
  `imagename` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '博主头像路径',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- ----------------------------
-- Records of t_blogger
-- ----------------------------
